{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_liu_feng_gu","speaker_name":"柳风骨","listener":null,"text":"无色来了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_niang","speaker_name":"王大娘","listener":null,"text":"你怎么知道是他来了？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"来的一共有三个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_liu_feng_gu","speaker_name":"柳风骨","listener":null,"text":"旁边有两个人的脚步声很轻，你们听不出。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"这老和尚在上面穷兜圈子干什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_liu_feng_gu","speaker_name":"柳风骨","listener":null,"text":"他这是在向我们示威。","tone":"微笑","chapter":13,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"这么样说来，他莫非已知道有人在下面？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"但他却还没有找出到下面来的路。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"可是他迟早找得出来的，是不是？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_niang","speaker_name":"王大娘","listener":null,"text":"他既然已知道有人在下面，不找到我们，怎么肯走？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_niang","speaker_name":"王大娘","listener":null,"text":"但他若看到我们在下面，还是会起疑心的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"那么我们不如就快点走吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"我们不能走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"不能走就是不能走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"难道我们就这样在这里等着他找来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"我们也不必等。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"既不能走，也不必等，你说该怎么办呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"我上去找他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_niang","speaker_name":"王大娘","listener":null,"text":"你上去找他？你疯了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":13,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"他既已找到这里来，说不定已对这件事起了疑心，不查个水落石出，他是绝不肯放手的，所以……","tone":"沉声","chapter":13,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"所以怎么样？","tone":"焦急","chapter":13,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"所以我们就不如一不做，二不休，索性连他也……","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_niang","speaker_name":"王大娘","listener":null,"text":"你难道想连他也一起杀了灭口？","tone":"焦急","chapter":13,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"我们已杀了一个和尚，和尚又不是杀不得的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":13,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_zhang_hao_er","speaker_name":"张好儿","listener":null,"text":"问题是，谁去杀他呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_yang_fan","speaker_name":"杨凡","listener":null,"text":"我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":